@startuml Soccer Field Booking System - Communication Diagram: Create Booking

title Sơ đồ Giao tiếp - Tạo Đặt sân

actor ":Thành viên" as Member
participant ":BookingController" as BController
participant ":BookingService" as BService
participant ":FieldService" as FService
participant ":PaymentService" as PService
participant ":NotificationService" as NotiService
database ":Database" as DB
actor ":Hệ thống thanh toán" as PaymentGateway

' Links and messages with numbering indicating sequence
Member -> BController : 1: Yêu cầu đặt sân (POST /bookings)
BController -> BService : 2: createBooking(bookingDto)
BService -> FService : 2.1: checkAvailability(fieldId, time)
FService --> BService : 2.2: (true) Sân còn trống
BService -> DB : 2.3: Ghi Booking (status="PENDING")
DB --> BService : 2.4: bookingEntity (đã lưu)
BService -> PService : 2.5: initiatePayment(bookingEntity)
PService -> PaymentGateway : 2.5.1: Yêu cầu tạo giao dịch
PaymentGateway --> PService : 2.5.2: paymentUrl
PService --> BService : 2.6: paymentUrl
BService --> BController : 2.7: { bookingId, paymentUrl }
BController --> Member : 3: 201 Created (Chuyển hướng)

' Second part of the flow (webhook confirmation)
PaymentGateway -> BController : 4: Gửi thông báo thanh toán thành công (Webhook /payments/webhook)
BController -> PService : 5: handleSuccessfulPayment(paymentData)
PService -> DB : 5.1: Cập nhật Payment (status="SUCCESS")
DB --> PService : 5.2: paymentEntity (đã cập nhật)
PService -> BService : 5.3: confirmBooking(bookingId)
BService -> DB : 5.3.1: Tìm Booking theo bookingId
DB --> BService : 5.3.2: bookingToConfirm
BService -> BService : 5.3.3: bookingToConfirm.confirm()
BService -> DB : 5.3.4: Cập nhật Booking (status="CONFIRMED")
BService -> NotiService : 5.3.5: sendBookingConfirmation(bookingToConfirm)
NotiService --> BService : 5.3.6:
BService --> PService : 5.4:
PService --> BController : 5.5:
BController --> PaymentGateway : 6: 200 OK (Phản hồi webhook)

@enduml
